Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: I’m sorry you’re suffering and feeling unseen. I hope there are people in your life who are willing to see. You may need to communicate with words rather than asking them to intuit the oblique poetry of suffering from your body but I very much hope they will hear, and care, and help <3   The hardest part for me has been coming to terms with the reality that in the end, no amount of other people caring can fill the void left by me not caring.

Author: katarina-stratford
Text: Ayee. Got to my personal absolute dream gw this week. No ones even blinked.
